{"tid":607220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《戰狼2》外交部：公民不聽勸前往危險地區　國家不免費救","createTime":"2018-03-27T06:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T11:37:13.000Z","uid":54373,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"383d66ef14a1890ae60898596420f2165eefeeb9","tid":607220,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:27:33.000Z","msg":"【外交部：公民不聽勸前往危險地區　國家不免費救】<br />\n<br />\n外交部3月26日發布《中華人民共和國領事保護與協助工作條例（草案）》（徵求意見稿），公開徵求社會意見。其中規定，中國公民應當密切關注欲前往國家或已在國家的有關安全提醒，加強安全防範，合理安排海外行程。中國公民在相應安全提醒發布後仍堅持前往有關高風險國家或地區的，因協助而產生的費用由個人承擔。"},{"pid":"8c0908382ec2903039e0f8f371466bdd4e186bcd","tid":607220,"uid":13257,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"又話護照背後有一個強大嘅國家嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d3f88bb37e53dbe718840791aec903e0c0efd1","tid":607220,"uid":63909,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"大陸LOGIC 正確喎<br />\n<br />\n你死你賤"},{"pid":"6873f2b4bed084a14af18fef45c066f7556fe2c9","tid":607220,"uid":54373,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.21so.com/wxtest/20170805/dyi1tjbtpkqgetImage.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.21so.com%2Fwxtest%2F20170805%2Fdyi1tjbtpkqgetImage.jpg&h=240186a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2eca55ff7a76451212ac0d090693f2f881ab3b20","tid":607220,"uid":41914,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"8c0908382ec2903039e0f8f371466bdd4e186bcd","tid":607220,"uid":13257,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTi